621
00:45:05,830 --> 00:45:08,100
Some honey.

622
00:45:08,330 --> 00:45:12,460
The pride of the Duchy of Urbino.

623
00:45:12,700 --> 00:45:15,360
Oh, I've made arrangements with their duke.

624
00:45:17,060 --> 00:45:20,030
With rawn like his, I pity those who wish harm upon Florence.

625
00:45:20,230 --> 00:45:22,400
